{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"0679c73d8b13f2f180cebb20bab9750d","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. I have all the patterns. Now let me create F-201: API `/api/akasha/mandato-do-dia`.\n\nPlan:\n1. Create `apps/akasha-portal/src/app/api/akasha/mandato-do-dia/route.ts` (GET endpoint)\n2. It accepts optional `?intencao=...` query param\n3. Authenticates user via `requireAkashaApi`\n4. Loads user (for birthDate, birthTime, birthTimezone) and birthChart\n5. If no birthChart → 404\n6. If no user birth data → 400 (cannot calculate)\n7. Builds AkashaInput\n8. Calls `calcular(input)` from `@akasha/core`\n9. Returns `{ date, escala, pilares_relevantes, redacao_bruta, cita_fontes, mentor_hook }` JSON\n10. Edge: crisis detected → returns 200 with `recurso: 'CVV-188'` (don't 4xx, but also don't process via LLM)\n\nLet me also add a test in `tests/api/akasha/mandato-do-dia/route.test.ts`.\n\nLet me write the route.","signature":"2db36c1975586fc8309397f81ad976676b0b81dd3911ab6c8fea29ccd8ae4a0d"}],"model":"MiniMax-M3","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard"},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"57d2ecb7-0101-4087-a0d9-0837b2dd3247","uuid":"0147dc7d-7c96-4e5d-8a42-d517a2c2af62"}
